justification.machine_selection: 4-axis Turn-Mill center selected due to:       - Complex part with multiple conical and cylindrical features       - High precision requirements       - Need for both turning and milling operations       - Material is stainless steel requiring rigid setup
setup_considerations: Multiple precision surfaces needing careful alignment
justification.cutting_parameters: Using carbide tooling with:       - Turning: Vc=120-150 m/min, f=0.2-0.25 mm/rev       - Milling: Vc=80-100 m/min, fz=0.05-0.08 mm/tooth       - Conservative parameters for stainless steel
